          impact: 'OSCP is the most respected hands-on penetration testing certification in the industry. Unlike multiple-choice exams, it cannot be passed by memorization — it requires actually compromising machines under time pressure. Employers in offensive security treat it as proof of practical skill. It is frequently listed as a requirement or strong preference for penetration tester, red team operator, and vulnerability researcher roles.',
